translations: [生物][化学]同系物（homologue 的复数）；同系化合物

sentences.sentence: Results of this study would form a base to quantify curcuminoid homologues by C30-HPLC-PDA.
sentences.translation: 本研究的结果奠定了应用C30-HPLC-PDA定量检测类姜黄素同系物的基础。

sentences.sentence: In this article the regularity of amino acid replacement among homologues insulins was explored.
sentences.translation: 本文研究了同源胰岛素间氨基酸取代的规律性。

sentences.sentence: OBJECTIVE To extract the polyprenol homologues from Ginkgo biloba leaves and optimize the separation process.
sentences.translation: 目的从银杏叶中提取聚戊烯醇同系物并对其提取工艺进行优化。
